section.p:
Same triples but in the standard Turtle syntax, the most common and convenient
				way to write RDF by
				hand:@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/> .
@prefix ex: <http://example.com/family/> .

<http://elandais.fr/eric> foaf:givenName "Eric" ;
	ex:isInLoveWith <http://elandais.fr/olga> .
<http://elandais.fr/salomé> rdf:type ex:Female .
